{"tid":980971,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"垃圾球員賤種朗 真正垃圾實力update 20190114","createTime":"2019-01-14T01:29:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T05:12:22.000Z","uid":54373,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c28e4784c86351628918c14cb0abf4b3dddb6f44","tid":980971,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T01:29:18.000Z","msg":"今場波豪比賤種朗,因為無網站出意盃數據,所以唔計佢<br />\n因為條垃圾淪落到意盃唔係決賽都照踢,不過垃圾此終垃圾<br />\n垃圾時間62分鐘入場,1球都入唔到<br />\n<br />\n本週<br />\n賤種朗 - n射0入<br />\n美斯 - 2射1入<br />\n<br />\n#數據post目的係唔想班賤朗迷再呃人<br />\n#上述數據由今季第1場比賽開始計算<br />\n#上述數據根據 who scored + 7m 賽後數據 每場累積而來<br />\n<br />\n賤種朗<br />\n聯賽: 125射14入球 (4球靠12碼) (11.2%)<br />\n歐聯: 27射1入球 1紅牌 (3.7%)<br />\n意大利盃: n射0入 (190113vs 榜尾博洛尼亞, 沒有數據,豪比佢唔計)<br />\n已射152球 得個15個入球 合共9.8%<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美斯<br />\n聯賽: 80射17入球 (1球靠12碼) (21.3%)<br />\n歐聯: 20射6入球 0紅牌 (30%)<br />\n100射入23球 合共23%"},{"pid":"5de439540897e36b657a98539c122a273fd6a032","tid":980971,"uid":77606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T01:38:24.000Z","msg":"早晨 騎哥又咁早<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b29fa6b6374bec6023dd5df0a5d57af68bbe64c","tid":980971,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5de439540897e36b657a98539c122a273fd6a032","tid":980971,"uid":77606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T01:38:24.000Z","msg":"早晨 騎哥又咁早<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T01:39:47.000Z","msg":"搵極都無意盃數據<br />\n<br />\n當豪比佢,反正計少場,美斯都拋離佢"},{"pid":"b0d246336382c83fc33cc180c